<P><HI>Have all nouns the &s;ingular number?</HI> The following nouns, from the nature of the things they expre&s;s, are u&s;ed only in the plural num|ber; viz.
<LIST>
<ITEM>Aborigines</ITEM>
<ITEM>aloes</ITEM>
<ITEM>alms</ITEM>
<ITEM>amends</ITEM>
<ITEM>annals</ITEM>
<ITEM>archives</ITEM>
