</DIV3>
<DIV3 TYPE="mode">
<HEAD>POTENTIAL MODE.</HEAD>
<P>Pre&s;ent. Ab&s;olute.</P>
<P><LIST>
<ITEM>I may, thou maye&s;t, he may</ITEM>
<ITEM>I can, thou can&s;t, he can</ITEM>
<ITEM>I mu&s;t, thou mu&s;t, he mu&s;t</ITEM>
