<P>And Rebekah took goodly <HI>raiment</HI> of her eld|e&s;t &s;on <HI>which was</HI> with her in the hou&s;e, and put <HI>it</HI> upon Jacob her young|e&s;t &s;on. By ibid and 5.</P>
