</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="corrections">
<P><HI>Soone&s;t</HI> and <HI>often</HI> are ad|verbs and ought not to be placed before nouns like adjectives.</P>
<P><HI>Quicke&s;t</HI> and <HI>frequent</HI> would be employed with more propriety.</P>
</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="errors">
<PB N="100" REF="018871_0099_0FA820DC652EA958">
<HEAD>Other Improprieties.</HEAD>
